
<h1>ep&#183ic - heroic; majestic; impressively great</h1>
<br>
<h2>Our generation is all too familiar with hyperbole, however, we all understand that when a cappella music is great, there is no other word for it but "epic".</h2>

<br>
<h3 align="left">September 12th, 2013</h3>
<p align="left" class="big"><i>Epic</i> is a new a cappella studio servicing Los Angeles and the internet! We provide custom a cappella arrangements for all-female and co-ed groups of any age. We also want to build an online resource for a cappella music directors by providing a place for the community to post questions, offer wisdom, and create discussion. Have ideas or questions to submit? Get in touch!

<br><br>What's new? We're currently setting up a brand new a cappella recording and editing studio in West Los Angeles for groups on a budget. Check back for details...</p>
